EXT. ROOFTOP - NIGHT

SARAH sprints across the gravel. Behind her, FOOTSTEPS.

She reaches the edge. Looks down. **Ten stories.**

SARAH
(to herself)
Don't think. Just jump.

She backs up. Runs. LEAPS--

